description:
Learn what Energy Medicine is, how it works, and how YOU can begin to implement it in your life today!

- Topics include Energy, Energy Medicine, Meditation, Thoughts and Emotions, Qi, Vibration, Chakras, Checking your Chakras, and Passion.

- The course includes 10 energy exercises that you will experience as well as printable handouts and worksheets.

- After completion of the course you will know in which area you should personally employ energy medicine for yourself and which energetic practices to use.

So, say YES to empowering yourself for greater wellness and take this course today!
title: Do It Yourself Energy Medicine
